# File Identification

\Marker id
\TextType Other
\TextProperties paragraph nonpublishable nonvernacular book
\Name File - ID
\Description The ID line - usually includes 3 letter ID keyboarder, edit date
\StyleType Paragraph
\FontSize 10

\Marker cc
\TextType Other
\TextProperties paragraph nonpublishable nonvernacular
\OccursUnder id
\Name File - Consistent Changes Scripts run on the text
\Description The CC Line - cct name, date run, text programmer
\StyleType Paragraph
\FontSize 10
\Rank 1

\Marker h
\TextType Other
\TextProperties paragraph publishable nonvernacular
\Rank 1
\OccursUnder id
\Name File - Running Header
\Description The text to use for the running header for this book
\StyleType Paragraph
\FontSize 10
\TEStyleName Header & Footer

